{name} this is Kerubo from clinic. Hope you are well. We can ensure your babies are growing. When is your next visit? Do you have questions for the nurse?

{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Natumaini wewe unahisi vizuri. Tunaweza kuhakikisha kuwa mtoto wako anakuwa vizuri. Je ziara yako inayofuata nilini? Je uko na maswali ya kuuliza muuguzi?
{name} this is Kerubo from clinic. Hope you are well. We can ensure your baby is growing. When is your next visit? Do you have questions for the nurse?

{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Natumaini wewe unahisi vizuri. Kliniki yaweza kuhakikisha kuwa mtoto wako anakuwa vizuri. Tafadhali kuja kwa ziara zako za kliniki ya wajawazito ili tuweze kukufuatilia.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. I hope you are feeling well. The clinic can make sure your baby is growing well. Please come in for your ANC visits so we can monitor you.
Ni Muhimu zaidi wewe kuja kwa ziara zako ili tuweze kukufuatilia. Wakati kuna watoto wawili kuko na hatari zaidi.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Natumaini wewe unahisi vizuri. Kliniki yaweza kuhakikisha kuwa watoto wako wanakuwa vizuri.
It is most important that you come in for your visit so we can monitor you. When there are two babies there is more risk.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. I hope you are feeling well. The clinic can make sure your babies are growing well.

{name}, mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki. Umefanya kazi nzuri kwa kuja kwa ajili ya ziara yako ya leo. Unahitaji kuwa na angalau ziara 4 wakati wa ujauzito wako. Utauliza familia yako ikusaidie kufika huko.
{name},  it is Kerubo from clinic. Good job coming in for your visit today. You will need at least 4 visits during pregnancy. Ask your family to help you get there.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. Having a surgery for your baby makes the second delivery more dangerous. Delivery at the hospital could save your baby's life.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kwa kliniki ya Mathare. Baada ya upasuaji kwa ajili ya mtoto wako hufanya kuzaa kwa mtoto wa pili hatari zaidi. Kuzaa hospitalini kunaweza kuokoa maisha ya mtoto wako.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. Each labor is different. If something goes wrong with labor @ home it may be too late for help.
The hospital can monitor you & your baby. Don't wait to come in. We can help you!
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kwa kliniki ya Mathare. Kila kuzaa ni tofauti. Kama kitu fulani kitaenda vibaya na kazaa nyumbani unaweza kuchelewa kupata msaada.
Hospitali inaweza kufuatilia wewe na watoto wako. Usisubiri kuja ndani. Tunaweza kukusaidia!
{name} this is Kerubo from clinic. It is safest to deliver your baby at the hospital. In an emergency at home it will be too late to get help.
There are always nurses here to help you. Please talk to your nurse about where you should deliver your baby.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kwa kliniki ya Mathare. Ni salama kabisa kuzaa mtoto wako katika hospitali. Kukiwa na dharura na unazaa nyumbani unaweza kuchelewa kuchelewa kupata msaada.
Hapa daima kuna wauguzi wa kukusaidia. Tafadhali zungumza na muuguzi wako mahali ambapo unapaswa kuzaa mtoto wako.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. Put a little money aside each week to have your baby in a safe place. Because of your surgery, you will need to have your baby in a hospital.
It will be very dangerous for you to have your baby at home. We are here to help.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kwa kliniki ya Mathare. Weka pesa kidogo kando kila wiki ili uzae mtoto wako katika mahali salama. Kwa sababu ya upasuaji uliofanyiwa, unahitaji kuzaa katika hospitali.
Itakuwa ni hatari sana kwa wewe kuzaa nyumbani. Sisi tulo hapa kusaidia.

{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Unapaswa kuwa na uchungu wa uzazi hivi karibuni. Tafadhali wasiliana kwa kutuandikia wakati unapojifungua watoto wako. Sisi tuna furaha sana kwa ajili yako!
{name} this is Kerubo from the ANC clinic. Breastfeeding a baby right after birth helps the milk come.
The first yellow sticky milk has many vitamins & cleans out the stomach. Milk has all the water the baby needs, avoid other liquids.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Kunyonyesha mtoto baada tu ya kuzaliwa husaidia maziwa kuja.
Maziwa ya kwanza ya njano inayo nata ina vitamini nyingi na ina safisha tumbo. Maziwa yana maji yote ambayo mtoto wanahitaji, epuka kupeana vinywaji vingine.
{name} this is Kerubo from clinic. Bad swelling of hands and face or a bad headache are signs of a problem. This is more common when you have two babies
Ask your family to take you to the clinic if you have bad swelling or headaches.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Uvimbe mbaya wa mikono na uso au maumivu mabaya ya kichwa ni dalili ya tatizo. Hii ni zaidi wakati una watoto wawili
Uliza familia yako wakupeleke kliniki kama una uvimbe mbaya au maumivu ya kichwa.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. When you come in for labour, we will give you a birth notification.
Delivery at the hospital could save your babies lives.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Wakati wewe unapokuja kwa ajili ya kuzaa, tutakupa karatasi ya kuthibitisha kuzaliwa.
Kuzaa katika hosipitali kunaweza kuokoa maisha ya watoto wako.

{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. Regular, strong stomach pains are a sign of labour. If you feel strong tightening of your belly, leaking of fluid or any bleeding go to the clinic. Don't wait.

{name} mimi Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Mara kwa mara, maumivu ya makubwa ya tumbo ni ishara ya kuzaa. Kama wewe utahisi tumbo lako lina jikaza, kuvuja maji au kuvuja kitu chochote kwenda kliniki. Usisubiri.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. Each labor is different. If something goes wrong with labor @ home it may be too late for help.
The hospital can monitor you & your babies. Don't wait to come in. We can help you!
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Kila kuzaa ni tofauti. Kama kitu fulani kitaenda vibaya na kazaa nyumbani unaweza kuchelewa kupata msaada.
hospitali inaweza kufuatilia wewe na watoto wako. Usisubiri kuja ndani. Tunaweza kukusaidia!
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. The Implant is a small rod with medicine for family planning. It is placed in your arm and is very effective for 3 years.
The Implant can be removed at any time! Ask about the Implant at the next visit and it may be low cost or free!
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Implant ni kijiti kidogo kilichoko na dawa ya mpango wa uzazi. Kinawekwa ndani ya mkono wako na ni madhubuti kwa miaka mitatu.
implant inaweza kuondolewa wakati wowote! Uliza kuhusu implant katika ziara ifuatayo na inaweza kuwa ya bei nafuu au kupewa bila kulipa.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. The IUCD or coil is a small device for family planning.
Easy to put in, safe and very effective for years the IUCD or coil can be removed at any time! Ask about the coil at the next visit and it may be low cost or free!
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. IUCD au koili ni kifaa kidogo cha mpango wa uzazi.

Rahisi kukiweka, ni salama na kina ufanisi wa miaka mingi IUCD au koili inaweza kuondolewa wakati wowote! Uliza kuhusu koili katika ziara ifutayo na ni inaweza kuwa ya bei nafuu au kupewa bila kulipa.

{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. It is best to think about family planning before you have your baby and have a plan in place, especially because you are having two babies. We will send you information about options.

{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Ni bora kufikiri kuhusu mpango wa uzazi kabla ya kupata mtoto wako na kuwa na mpango uliouchagua, hasa kwa sababu wewe uko na watoto wawili. Sisi tutakutumia habari kuhusu mipango mingi ya uzazi.
{name} this is Kerubo from clinic. It is safest to deliver your babies at hospital. In an emergency at home it may be too late to get help.
There are always nurses here to help you. Please talk to your nurse about where you should deliver your babies.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Ni salama kabisa kuzaa watoto wako katika kliniki au hospitali. Katika hali ya dharura ukiwa nyumbani unaweza kuchelewa kupata msaada.
Daima hapa kuna wauguzi wa kukusaidia. Tafadhali zungumza na muuguzi wako kuhusu mahali ambapo unapaswa kuzaa watoto wako.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. I hope you are feeling well. The clinic can make sure your babies are growing well.
It is most important that you come in for your visit so we can monitor you. When there are two babies there is more risk.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Natumaini wewe unahisi vizuri. Kliniki yaweza kuhakikisha kuwa watoto wako wanakuwa vizuri.
Ni Muhimu zaidi wewe kuja kwa ziara zako ili tuweze kukufuatilia. Wakati kuna watoto wawili kuko na hatari zaidi.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. The cost of having your baby at the hospital is now free. Put a little money aside each week to have your babies in a safe place. We are here to help.

{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Gharama ya kuzaa mtoto wako katika Mathare sasa ni bure. Weka pesa kidogo kando kila wiki ili upate watoto wako mahali salama. Sisi tuko hapa kusaidia.
{name} this is Kerubo from clinic. You need iron because it keeps blood doing its job carrying nutrition to your babies. If it is low, you feel tired. We can give you tablets at your visit.

{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Unahitaji madili ya iron kwasababu hufanya damu kutekeleza kaziyake ya kubeba lishe kwenda kwa watoto wako. Kama ni ya chini, unaweza kujisikia mchovu. Tunaweza kukupatia dawa hizi wakati wa ziara zako.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. Try to have a plan in place to get to the clinic when you have labor pains. Save a little money each week for transport in labor.
It is especially important with two babies to have a clear plan to arrive at the hospital. Talk to your family about a plan.

{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Jaribu kuwa na mpango tayari wa kukuwezesha kufika kliniki wakati utakapokuwa una uchungu wa uzazi. Weka pesa kidogo kila wiki za usafiri wakati wa kuzaa.
Ni muhimu hasa kama uko na watoto wawili kuwa na mpango wa wazi wa kufika katika hospitali. Ongea na familia yako kuhusu mpa huo.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. If you have bleeding during this time in pregnancy go to the clinic right away. Don't wait. We can help!
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Kama wewe utatokwa na damu wakati huu wa mimba nenda kliniki haraka. Usisubiri. Tunaweza kusaidia!
{name} this is Kerubo from clinic. You can protect your babies from the tetanus infection. If you have not received injections for tetanus, ask the nurse for the injection at your next visit.

{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Unaweza kulinda mtoto wako kutokana na maambukizi ya pepopunda. Kama wewe hujapata sindano kwa ajili ya pepopunda, mulize muuguzi akudunge sindano hiyo katika ziara yako ifuatayo.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. A burning pain at the top of your stomach is heartburn. Spicy foods can make it worse.
Milk may help soothe heartburn. This is more common with two babies. Ask your nurse if you are having bad pain.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Maumivu ya kuchoma juu ya tumbo yako ni kiungulia. Vyakula vyenye viungo vingi vinaweza kufanya hali hiyo kuwa mbaya zaidi.
Maziwa yanaweza kusaidia kutuliza kiungulia. Hii ni kawaida kwa watu wenye watoto wawili. Mulize muuguzi wako kama una maumivu mbaya.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. You'll start feeling the babies move soon. Take time everyday to feel them move. Tell your nurse if the movements decrease.

{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Hivi karibuni utaanza kuhisi mtoto akisonga songa. Kuwa na wakati kila siku wa kusikiza mtoto akisonga songa. Mwambie muuguzi wako kama kusonga songa kutatapungua.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. Drink plenty of clean water throughout the day. It can help prevent infections. Try to have 8 glasses a day.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Kunywa maji masafi mengi siku yote. Inaweza kusaidia kuzuia maambukizi. Jaribu kunywa gilasi 8 kwa siku.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. Please tell us if you need help or advice. We are here for you and your babies.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kliniki ya Mathare. Tafadhali tuambie kama unahitaji msaada au ushauri. Sisi tuko hapa kwa ajili yako na mtoto wako.
{name} this is Kerubo from the ANC clinic. Your babies will receive important vaccines at the next visit.
Please be sure to check your book and make sure your babies has all (his or her) vaccines. Ask your nurse to help check the book.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kwa kliniki ya wajawazito. Watoto wako watapata chanjo muhimu katika ziara ifuatayo.
Tafadhali hakikisha umeangalia kitabu chako na kuhakikisha watoto wako wana pata chanjo zote (zake). Muulize muuguzi wako akusaidie kuangalia kitabu.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. After birth you will bleed like a period on and off, so be prepared. Tell your nurse if you pass big clots.

{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kwa kliniki ya Mathare. Baada ya kuzaa utatokwa na damu kama damu ya mwezi mara kwa mara, kwahivyo kuwa tayari. Mwambie muuguzi wako kama utatokwa na damu ya kuganda kubwa.
{name} this is Kerubo from clinic. Are you having trouble breastfeeding? Giving babies other fluids can cause illness and weakness.
Please continue to only give breast milk to your babies for at least six month.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kwa kliniki. Je uko na matatizo ya kunyonyesha? Kupeana watoto maji au vinwaji vyengine kunaweza kusababisha ugonjwa na udhaifu.
Tafadhali endelea kupeana maziwa ya mama kwa watoto wako kwa miezi sita.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. The Implant is a small rod with medicine for family planning. It is placed in your arm and is very effective for 3 years.
The Implant can be removed at any time! Ask about the Implant at the next visit and it may be low cost or free!
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kwa kliniki ya Mathare. Implant ni kijiti kindogo kilichoko na dawa ya mpango wa uzazi. Kinawekwa ndani ya mkono wako na ni madhubuti kwa miaka mitatu.
implant inaweza kuondolewa wakati wowote! Uliza kuhusu implant katika ziara ifuatayo na inaweza kuwa ya bei nafuu au kupewa bila kulipa.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. The IUCD or coil is a small device for family planning.
Easy to put in, safe and very effective for years the IUCD or coil can be removed at any time! Ask about the coil at the next visit and it may be low cost or free!
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kwa kliniki ya Mathare. IUCD au koili ni kifaa kidogo cha mpango wa uzazi.

Rahisi kukiweka, ni salama na kina ufanisi wa miaka mingi IUCD au koili inaweza kuondolewa wakati wowote! Uliza kuhusu koili katika ziara ifutayo na ni inaweza kuwa ya bei nafuu au kupewa bila kulipa.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. It is best to think about family planning before you go to the clinic and have a plan in place.
We will send you information about options. Please talk to the nurse about family planning at the next visit. It is best to space you babies.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kwa kliniki ya Mathare. Ni bora kufikiri kuhusu mpango wa uzazi kabla ya kwenda kliniki na kuwa na mpango uliouchagua.
Sisi tutakutumia habari kuhusu mipango ya uzazi. Tafadhali zungumza na muuguzi kuhusu mpango wa uzazi katika ziara inayofuata. Ni bora kupata mtoto mmoja hadi mwengine baada ya mda.
{name} this is Kerubo from the ANC clinic. Your babies will receive important vaccines at the next visit.
Please be sure to check your book and make sure your babies have all the vaccines. Ask your nurse to help check the book.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kwa kliniki ya wajawazito. Watoto wako watapata chanjo muhimu katika ziara ifuatayo.
Tafadhali hakikisha umeangalia kitabu chako na kuhakikisha watoto wako wana pata chanjo zote. Muulize muuguzi wako akusaidie kuangalia kitabu.
{name} this is Kerubo from clinic. Are you having trouble breastfeeding? Come to clinic we can help. Breast milk is the best gift to give your babies.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kwa kliniki. Uko na matatizo ya kunyonyesha? Kuja kliniki tunaweza kukusaidia. Maziwa ya matiti ni zawadi bora ya kuwapa watoto wako.
{name} this is Kerubo from Mathare clinic. If your new babies are having trouble breathing or feeding, is too warm, or very sleepy, go to the clinic.
{name} mimi ni Kerubo kutoka kwa kliniki ya Mathare. Kama watoto wako wapya wako na matatizo ya kupumua au kunyonya, wako na joto sana, au wana usingizi sana, nenda kliniki.
